steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
Debug step:
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jitdash005" and Comment "Testing"
When I navigate to menu "Dashboard app" without submenu
Then I should see Dashboard screen display
Then I should see table Name "jitdash005" displayed in dashboard list
When I select table Name "jitdash005" in dashboard table list
When I toggle on switcher of item "Update of" with table Name "jitdash005"
Then I should see option value "jitdash005s.updated_at,jitdash005s.created_at" displayed in multi dropdown menu label "Params to request" index "1" of item "Update of" with table Name "jitdash005"
When I select multi dropdown label "Params to request" index "1" of item "Update of" with table Name "jitdash005" by value "jitdash005s.created_at"
Then I should see option value "jitdash005s.updated_at" displayed in multi dropdown menu label "Params to request" index "1" of item "Update of" with table Name "jitdash005"
Then I should NOT see option value "jitdash005s.created_at" displayed in multi dropdown menu label "Params to request" index "1" of item "Update of" with table Name "jitdash005"
When I clear selected option value "jitdash005s.created_at" with index "1"
Then I should NOT see option value "jitdash005s.created_at" with index "1" displayed
Then I should see option value "jitdash005s.updated_at,jitdash005s.created_at" displayed in multi dropdown menu label "Params to request" index "1" of item "Update of" with table Name "jitdash005"
When I click general any span text button label "Select Table Columns" with index "1"

When I clear selected option value "jitdash005s.created_at,jitdash005s.updated_at" with index "1"
